"                             |VVVVVV|++++++++/VVVVV/'
"                             |VVVVVV|++++++/VVVVV/'
"                            +|VVVVVV|++++/VVVVV/'+
"                          +++|VVVVVV|++/VVVVV/'+++++
"                        +++++|VVVVVV|/VVVVV/'+++++++++
